"It is strongly recommended to install and configure the SIP proxy before "
"attempting a SIP PBX setup. The SIP proxy normalizes a lot of the traffic "
"reaching the PBX and provides greater connectivity and resilience."
msgstr ""
"به شدت توصیه می‌شود که قبل از راه‌اندازی SIP PBX ابتدا پروکسی آن را پیکربندی "
